1) Put in any folder
2) Install nodejs
https://nodejs.org/en/download/

3) Install npm
https://www.npmjs.com/get-npm

4) command line (cmd) on directory "client" 
cd Drive-letter:/any-path-name/any-folder-name/client/

5) execute the command "npm start" without comma

7) go to url: localhost:3000/

Note:
If you want on React Production Site, execute the command "npm run build" without comma and go to url: localhost:5000/
